Class MainController

java.lang.Object
com.gyp1.inventorymgtapp.MainController
All Implemented Interfaces:
javafx.fxml.Initializable
public class MainController extends Object implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
The MainController controls the main view and provides linkage to the PartController and ProductController.
